uration=\"200,2000\" data-anim-loop=\"yes\">\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"wpr-anim-text-inner\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Customers<\/b>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"wpr-anim-text-cursor\">|<\/span>\t\t<\/span>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t<\/h3>\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-c4ffcff elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no\" data-id=\"c4ffcff\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-fa26353\" data-id=\"fa26353\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e140be6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"e140be6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>1. Refund Eligibility<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Refunds are only applicable in specific situations, as outlined in this policy.<\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">To be eligible for a refund, you must have a valid and documented reason that falls within the scope of our refund policy.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>2. Eligible Refund Situations<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">We may consider issuing a refund in the following situations:<\/span><\/p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>a. Service Not Rendered<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">If, for any reason, we fail to provide the doorstep vehicle cleaning service for which you have made payment, a full refund will be issued.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>b. Unsatisfactory Service Quality<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Daily Cleaning service :<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">If you are not satisfied with the quality of the cleaning service provided, you must report your concerns to us within one hour&nbsp;after the service is completed.<\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">We will assess the validity of your claim and, if substantiated, may offer a partial or full refund at our discretion for that day.<\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">We will refund for missing day of cleaning.<\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">If our partner losses key of your vehicle , we will bear cost of that.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>3. Non-Eligible Refund Situations<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Refunds will not be provided in the following situations:<\/span><\/p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>a. No-Show or Late Cancellation<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">If you fail to be present or cancel your appointment with less than 24hr notice, no refund will be issued.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>b. Customer&#39;s Change of Mind<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Refunds will not be provided due to a change of mind or circumstances on the part of the customer.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>4. Requesting a Refund<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">To request a refund, please follow these steps:<\/span><\/p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Contact our customer support team at hello@vehiclean.in within 24hrs of the service completion or issue.<\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Provide a detailed explanation of the reason for your refund request, along with any supporting evidence if applicable.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>5. Refund Processing<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Once we receive your refund request, we will review it promptly.<\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">If your request is approved, we will initiate the refund process. The method of refund will be the same as the original payment method whenever possible.<\/span><\/li>\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Refunds may take 7-10 business days&nbsp;to process and reflect in your account.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>6. Contact Us<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">If you have any questions or concerns about our refund policy or the refund process, please contact us at hello@vehiclean.in.<\/span><\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Refund policy for Customers | 1. Refund Eligibility Refunds are only applicable in specific situations, as outlined in this policy. To be eligible for a refund, you must have a valid and documented reason that falls within the scope of our refund policy. 2. Eligible Refund Situations We may consider issuing a refund in the &hellip;<\/p>\n<p class=\"read-more\"> <a class=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/vehiclean.in\/index.php\/refund-policy\/\"> <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Refund Policy<\/span> Read More &raquo;<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"site-sidebar-l